    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN366">
<l>viḻukkaṭip paṟainta muḻukuraṉ muraca</l>
<l>‍<supplied>moḻukkuṭai ma</supplied>ruṅki ṉorumoḻit tāka</l>
<l>varaveṟi yurumi ṉuraṟupu cilaippa</l>
<l>vorutā mākiya perumai yōrun</l>
<l>tampukaḻ niṟīic ceṉṟumāyn taṉarē</l>
<l>yataṉā laṟavōṉ makaṉē ma<supplied>ṟavōr cemmāl</supplied></l>
<l><gap quantity="26" reason="lost" unit="character"/>uraippak <supplied>kēṇmati</supplied></l>
<l>niṉṉūṟṟam piṟaraṟiyātu</l>
<l>piṟarkūṟiya moḻiteriyā</l>
<l>ñāyiṟ ṟellai yāḷviṉaik kutavi</l>
<l>yiravi ṉellai varuvatu nāṭi</l>
<l>yurai<gap quantity="41" reason="lost" unit="character"/></l>
<l>uḻavoḻi perumpaka ṭaḻitiṉ ṟāṅkuc</l>
<l>ceṅkaṇ makaḷiroṭu ciṟutuṉi yaḷaii</l>
<l>yaṅkaṭ ṭēṟa lāykalat tukuppak</l>
<l>keṭalarun tiruva<gap quantity="29" reason="lost" unit="character"/></l>
<l>maṭaivēṇṭunark kiṭaiyarukā</l>
<l>taviḻvēṇṭunark kiṭaiyaruḷi</l>
<l>viṭaivīḻttuc cūṭukiḻippa</l>
<l>nīrnilai perutta vārmaṇa laṭaikaraik</l>
<l>kāvutoṟum<gap quantity="26" reason="lost" unit="character"/></l>
<l>maṭaṅka luṇmai māyamō vaṉṟē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">While whole-voiced drums beaten by excellent sticks </l>
<l corresp="2">being of one word on the side of conduct(?) </l>
<l corresp="3">resounded, roaring like snake-attacking thunder, </l>
<l corresp="4">even great people who had become unique, </l>
<l corresp="5">having established their fame, went [and] vanished. </l>
<l corresp="6">Therefore, son of a righteous man, eminence among the brave, </l>
<l corresp="7">listen when talk………….. </l>
<l corresp="8">being unknown to others with respect to your strength, </l>
<l corresp="9">not understanding the words spoken by others, </l>
<l corresp="10">contributing to manly work within the boundaries of day, </l>
<l corresp="11">examining what comes within the boundaries of night, </l>
<l corresp="12">word………………………………. </l>
<l corresp="14">mingling in little disgust with red-eyed women, </l>
<l corresp="13">like a big bull that ceased ploughing eats straw, </l>
<l corresp="15">while they(?) pour fine toddy from choice vessels, </l>
<l corresp="16">fortune difficult to lose……………………. </l>
<l corresp="17">not stinting among those who want gifts, </l>
<l corresp="18">being gracious among those who want rice, </l>
<l corresp="19">while they(?) throw down a ram [and] tear the roast, </l>
<l corresp="20">on the compacted shore with overflowing sand where the position of the water rose, </l>
<l corresp="21">in every grove……………. </l>
<l corresp="22">is the existence of Death an illusion? It is not. </l>
</lg>
